| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4021 — Recovery Inhibition (everest)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f2bc7c9b-cb01-5d3b-be5b-1ede4794ed1c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
